    "updated_at": "2016-08-03T02:53:27Z",
    "body": "Remember that Squirrel.Windows always writes its shortcut targets as trampolines - i.e. it's not a shortcut to `MyApp.exe`, it's a shortcut to `Update.exe --processStart MyApp.exe` -  this means that even if an update fails to fix the shortcut, it still is clickable.\n\nhttps://github.com/Squirrel/Squirrel.Windows/blob/cedf4c296c830fcea09ff4ffca7cc1083b4ede67/src/Squirrel/UpdateManager.ApplyReleases.cs#L228\n"
  },
